				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I am new to the necromancer world (main is a druid). What focus effects are most useful for a necro and what spell lines to they improve? I believe that I had read that Improved Damage increases lifetaps. Does that make them heal you for more also? Does Improved Healing affect lifetaps or dots that take health and give to you or  just pet heals?
<br />
Any info would be greatly appreciated. Thanks a ton.
