			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">improved damage effects our nukes and lifetap. double dmg is also double selfheal.
<br />
in addition we got theft of life. which crits the heal portion only, so max is 4 times heal, if both foci crit same time. ToL also works on our pet heals.
<br />

<br />
improved healing does nothing for necs.
<br />
our dots  are affected by our dot foci only. you should know them as a druid.
<br />
the important foci are pretty much the same like for an offensive druid (no heal): AE4, BA4, ET4, AH4, ID4, SH4, MP4, ER4 .... etc.
<br />

<br />
read the guides on our homepage for more info.
<br />
<a href="http://necro.eqclasses.com/focus/focuslist.asp" target="_blank">http://necro.eqclasses.com/focus/focuslist.asp</a>
<br />

<br />

<br />
i move this question to newbie land, btw. it belongs there. and its a much safer place for druids <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="Wink" border="0" />
<br />

<br />

